# Copy this file to `.npmrc` and fill in your own Trimble Artifactory token.
# `.npmrc` is gitignored so the real token is never committed.
#
# How to get the token:
#   1. Log in to https://artifactory.trimble.tools
#   2. Artifacts -> repo `trimble-agentic-external-npm-local` -> "Set Me Up" (npm)
#      OR  avatar -> Edit Profile -> Generate an Identity Token
#   3. Paste the token below in place of YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN.

@trimble-agentic-external-npm-local:registry=https://artifactory.trimble.tools/artifactory/api/npm/trimble-agentic-external-npm-local/
//artifactory.trimble.tools/artifactory/api/npm/trimble-agentic-external-npm-local/:_authToken=YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN
//artifactory.trimble.tools/artifactory/api/npm/trimble-agentic-external-npm-local/:email=YOUR_TRIMBLE_EMAIL
//artifactory.trimble.tools/artifactory/api/npm/trimble-agentic-external-npm-local/:always-auth=true
